BUT NOT KNOWING WHERE WE ARE IN

18:01.480 --> 18:03.616
THE CHRONOLOGY OF THIS EVENT IS

18:03.616 --> 18:04.951
REALLY FRUSTRATING AND KINDA

18:04.951 --> 18:07.186
SCARY.

18:07.186 --> 18:08.721
>> Reporter: AFTER LEAVING

18:08.721 --> 18:10.423
SITKA, RAIMONDI AND MINER BEGAN

18:10.423 --> 18:13.125
RECEIVING DISTURBING REPORTS.

