THE HEALTHY-LOOKING STARS THEY

18:14.894 --> 18:16.629
CAREFULLY COUNTED JUST DAYS

18:16.629 --> 18:18.798
BEFORE WERE SUDDENLY LOSING ARMS

18:18.798 --> 18:21.100
AND WASTING AWAY.

